## UI targets (from specs)

- **GitHub PRSidebar:** shadow DOM in `#partial-discussion-sidebar`; Primer colors (`#1f2328`, `#d0d7de`, `#0969da`); remount on `turbo:load`.
- **Docs side panel:** Google Sans, `#202124` text, `#1a73e8` actions; enable on `docs.google.com` tabs.

## Adapter seam

`SyncAdapter` with `DirectAdapter` (empty `backend_url`) vs `BackendAdapter` (later). Do not couple feature code to DirectAdapter internals beyond the interface.
